---
title: Persian-Inspired Chickpea, Veggie and Chicken Tender Stew with Toasted Garlic Flatbreads
description: Middle Eastern spice-roasted carrots are the star of this warming tomato-based stew. Toasted almonds, chicken and a spicy chili-garlic sauce are the perfect toppers for this crave-worthy dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R1018_W20_CA_RV0409-3_Main__6low-fd159ae5.jpg
